&lt;h2 id="attracting-the-masses"&gt;Attracting the Masses&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brian Acton (WhatsApp cofounder) injected $50m into the Signal Foundation, allowing them to grow from 3 to 50 full-timers.&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;div class="comment-holder"&gt;
 &lt;div class="comment" title="Comment: tangential aside"&gt;&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;d think that at Signal&amp;rsquo;s dominance, getting $$$ shouldn&amp;rsquo;t be a problem. But VCs expect a multiple return and Signal doesn&amp;rsquo;t look like it will monetize soon.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>